{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 23:04:38.558561", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submitted the diagnosis:\n\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): web_server_0\n- Root cause(s): link_bandwidth_throttling\n\nRationale: qdisc netem 20ms delay and TBF shaper at 1 Mbit/s on web_server_0 eth0 introduced artificial delay and throughput cap, explaining elevated RTT/TTFB and skewed traffic when this backend is selected. Control plane and other infrastructure components appear healthy.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2123, "output_tokens": 98, "total_tokens": 2221, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2048}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
